Detailed Description

cvmx_uahc::_gdbgltssm

In multiport host configuration, the port number is defined by UAHC()_GDBGFIFOSPACE[SELECT]<3:0>. Value of this register may change immediately after reset. See description in UAHC()_GDBGFIFOSPACE.

This register can be reset by IOI reset or with UCTL()_CTL[UAHC_RST].
